Collaboration Smells (code smells)
	- Long method chains 
	- God objects 
	- Objects doing other's jobs 
	
Refactoring Checklist
	 - Can I move this method?
	 - Does this object know too much?
	 	- is it your bussiness to know everthing?
	 - Is this relationship necessary? 
	 
What You Just Learned 
	- Relationships shape design 
	- Collaboration drives behavior 
	- Encapsulation is enforced through structure 
	
Up Next!
